<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><span>在自己的作品内设置「作品问卷调查」的方法</span></h2>
<h2 id="h_01EJG84VP2JNZRTJRKF54FMMA2">电脑版</h2>
<h3>插画与漫画</h3>
<p><span>1.点选「作品问卷调查 - 响应关联作品 - 使用工具 - 描写内容」。</span></p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4402654309785/image10.png" alt="image10.png"></p>
<p><span>2.输入问题。</span></p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4402654321689/image4.png" alt="image4.png"><br><span>3.输入回答选项。</span></p>
<h3><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4402654331033/image9.png" alt="image9.png"></h3>
<h3>&nbsp;</h3>
<h3>动图</h3>
<p><span>1.勾选「作品问卷调查」的「设置」。</span></p>
<h3><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4402654384153/image7.png" alt="image7.png"></h3>
<p>2.即可输入问题与回答选项。</p>
<h3><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4402660385305/image12.png" alt="image12.png"></h3>
<h3>&nbsp;</h3>
<h3>小说</h3>
<p>1.点选「详细设置」。</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4402654413593/image17.png" alt="image17.png"></p>
<p>2.输入问题。</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4402660401049/image1.png" alt="image1.png"></p>
<p>3.输入回答选项。</p>
<h2><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4402654422425/image2.png" alt="image2.png"></h2>
<h2>&nbsp;</h2>
<h2 id="h_01EJG853FCYHXR2B96PWGH7YDA">手机版</h2>
<h3>插画、漫画与动图</h3>
<p>无法在手机版设置作品问卷调查。<br>若想设置问卷调查，请使用电脑版投稿作品。</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01EJG85BP17G2B5N1R21ERFMM0">小说</h3>
<p>1.点选「其他设置」。<br>2.开启「设置问卷」选项。<br>3..输入「问题」与「回答」。</p>
<p><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4402654451225/image14.png" alt="image14.png" width="324" height="542"></p>
<h3>&nbsp;</h3>
<h3 id="h_01EJG9X49AFSHTDYY6W8PXMANJ">APP版</h3>
<p><span>APP版无法设置作品问卷调查。</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

